cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.SI 

This paper focuses on natural language processing (NLP) and specifically on semantic change detection using contextualised embeddings. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves machine learning techniques, which could fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Information retrieval (cs.IR) is also relevant as the paper deals with analysing textual data. Finally, the paper proposes improvements to existing methods, which could fall under cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
